OL,3,CCan Glasgow afford to continue
OL,4,Cwelcoming refugees?
OL,6,FPressure has pushed the city into a
OL,7,Fhousing emergency, as ITV News
OL,8,FCorrespondent Peter Smith and Scotland
OL,9,FProducer Stephanie Docherty report
OL,11,FThe majority of all asylum seekers and
OL,12,Frefugees in Scotland are in Glasgow.
OL,14,FFor decades, its people and
OL,15,Fpoliticians have proudly promoted it
OL,16,Fas a sanctuary city that welcomes
OL,17,Feveryone, no matter where they come
OL,18,Ffrom.
OL,20,FBut that conscience is now coming with
OL,21,Fa cost.
