OL,3,CCan Glasgow afford to continue
OL,4,Cwelcoming refugees?
OL,6,FQasim is an asylum seeker from
OL,7,FAfghanistan. He came to the UK on a
OL,8,Fsmall boat earlier this year.
OL,10,FHe has just been moved to another
OL,11,Ftemporary home - this time to a two-
OL,12,Fbedroom flat which he will be sharing
OL,13,Fwith three men he has never met.
OL,15,FThere are no so-called asylum hotels
OL,16,Fin Glasgow, and instead, everyone is
OL,17,Fput into shared housing like this.
OL,19,F"I get moved around in Glasgow but as
OL,20,Fan asylum seeker I do get a home,"
OL,21,FQasim said.
