OL,6,F"If I get refugee status, I am made
OL,7,Fhomeless and then join a waiting list
OL,8,Ffor permanent accommodation. There are
OL,9,Fso many refugees here now it takes a
OL,10,Flong time.
OL,12,F"I was two years old when the UK
OL,13,Fbombed my country and told us to help
OL,14,Fthem fight the Taliban. My parents
OL,15,Fwere killed. If I go back, they will
OL,16,Fkill me too. The legal routes to come
OL,17,Fhere were all blocked. Going on a boat
OL,18,Fwas a risk I had to take."
