OL,6,F"(What) we're looking at is around a
OL,7,F#90 million budget gap for Glasgow,
OL,8,Fand about #66 million of that is
OL,9,Fhomelessness overspend," Council
OL,10,FLeader Susan Aitken said.
OL,12,FShe says this has been directly
OL,13,Fcreated by the large number of
OL,14,Fhomeless refugees.
OL,16,FShe says it is due to "the pressure of
OL,17,Fthe mass processing of people who are
OL,18,Frefugees already in the city and then
OL,19,Fexacerbated by people travelling from
OL,20,Fother parts of the UK".
