OL,6,FShe describes it as "a perfect storm"
OL,7,Fand says the council is now at the
OL,8,Fpoint where it is struggling to say
OL,9,Fthat refugees are welcome.
OL,11,F"That's not because we don't want to
OL,12,Fwelcome refugees. We want to be able
OL,13,Fto continue welcoming refugees. What
OL,14,Fwe're seeing is, if the UK government
OL,15,Fdoesn't step up to its
OL,16,Fresponsibilities and help us meet our
OL,17,Fresponsibilities, then that is going
OL,18,Fto become unsustainable. And it is
OL,19,Falready fast becoming unsustainable."
