OL,6,FIt's not just in the city chambers
OL,7,Fwhere attitudes are visibly changing.
OL,9,FScotland flags have begun appearing on
OL,10,Flampposts across the city,
OL,11,Fconcentrated in areas with large
OL,12,Fnumbers of asylum seekers and refugees.
OL,14,FThis is Scotland's contribution to the
OL,15,FRaise The Colours campaign seen in
OL,16,FEngland - partly patriotic pride,
OL,17,Fpartly an anti-immigration message to
OL,18,Fpoliticians.
